<P>That every Age is furni&s;ht with &s;ome remarkable in&s;tances hereof, may be <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">o keep up the credit of Chri&s;t's Death in the world; or to &s;hew that the value
